---

This repository vendors and derives symbol data from several upstream projects,
each redistributed under its own license (not the MIT license above):

  - unicode-math (unicode-math-table.tex) — LPPL v1.3c or later
  - W3C "XML Entity Definitions for Characters" (latex-symbols.tsv) — W3C license
  - leanprover/vscode-lean4 (lean-symbols.tsv) — Apache-2.0
  - rocq-prover/rocq (rocq-symbols.tsv) — LGPL-2.1-only

The Typst `sym` data is obtained at build time from the `codex` crate (Apache-2.0)
and is not vendored here. See `crates/unikodo-core/data/README.md` for details.
